- Follow AGENTS.md as the source of truth.
- Keep scope tight; do not add features not explicitly requested.
- Tenant isolation is mandatory: orgSlug is routing only, org_id is the security boundary.
- Every tenant-owned DB table must include org_id and have RLS enabled.
- Never trust client-provided org_id; derive org_id server-side.
- Staff requestors must NOT use client-side Supabase DB access; use server endpoints with requestor session cookie.
- Put business logic in /server. Keep React components/pages thin.
- Enforce job state transitions server-side and always write job_events.
- Use zod validation for inputs and return clear errors.
- Prefer minimal diffs; avoid large refactors unless asked.
- For every change, provide: list of files modified + manual test steps.